			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The key when you compare is to compare the AVERAGE, not the extreme.
<br />

<br />
A 7k Mana / 20 FT Mage is most likely doable with just 1 group stuff, but it sure aint the average, so not right to compare.
<br />

<br />
It's like taking the best equipped CoA+ Mage and comparing him to a crappy equipped lvl 65 twink saying that the item balance is just fine....<br />_________________<br />Master Elementalist Celecar - Magi - Forsaken Realm - Mithaniel Marr
<br />
Luterin - Ranger - Forsaken Realm - Mithaniel Marr</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
